com.google.javascript.rhino

Class Token

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.google.javascript.rhino.Token

  • public class Token
extends Object
    This class implements the JavaScript scanner. It is based on the C source files jsscan.c and jsscan.h in the jsref package.
